name: PrescribableNSAIDsAndAcuteMigraineAttackMedication
title: Prescribable NSAIDs and Acute Migraine Attack Medication
purpose: (Clinical Focus: The purpose of this value set is to represent concepts for acute migraine attack medication and prescribable non-steroidal anti-inflammatory drugs (NSAIDs).),(Data Element Scope: This value set may use a model element in the QDM category of medication.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes concepts that describe a prescribable NSAID medication or a medication specific to prescribable migraine medication.),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes concepts that describe over the counter NSAIDs.)
